Manx: “Slattys son ny sodjey mendeil Slattys son Jannoo oardaghyn son ny share sharaghey, glenney as foadey Straaidyn Ghoolish as son Jannoo as Karraghey Jeeigyn as Surmyn cadjin ayns shen as er aghtyn elley jannoo ny share stayd y valley cheddin.”
English: “An act for further ammending of the Act for Making orders for better improving, cleaning, and lighting the Streets of Douglas and for Mand and Repairing general Drains and Sewers there and in other ways making the state of said town better.”
